		<h2 class="comic-title">(New) X Force</h2>
		<p>The mutant race is near extinction and there are plenty of baddies who want to complete the job. Cyclops, as leader of the Xmen, organizes what can only be considered a secret hit squad called the X-Force. Targeting the most dire threats to mutant kind, they are deadly and proficient. This comic is exceptional in its gritty story and art.</p>

		<p><b>OMG Moment:</b> Archangel flips out and slaughters an army of altered human warriors called "The Choir". It was crazy.</p>